command of Capt. Fitz-Roy, R.N. 2nd edition, corrected,
with additions. 8vo. London, 1845. (Colonial and Home
Library.)

A Naturalist’s Voyage. Journal of
Researches, 8vo. London, 1860. [Contains a postscript
dated Feb. 1, 1860.]

